{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-series-article-tsx","path":"/articles/building-better-websites/part-2-implementation-development/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"f8a3c1ff-cd63-5698-8197-7e15f7f5477d","html":"<h1>Implementation &#x26; Development</h1>\n<p>Building on the planning and architecture from <strong>Part 1</strong>, we now move into the exciting implementation phase where ideas become reality.</p>\n<h2>Modern Development Workflow</h2>\n<p>Today's web development leverages powerful tools that streamline the development process:</p>\n<h3>Build Tools</h3>\n<p>Modern build tools like Vite, Webpack, and Parcel transform your source code into optimized bundles.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fast hot module replacement (HMR)</li>\n<li>Code splitting for optimal performance</li>\n<li>Tree shaking to eliminate dead code</li>\n<li>Asset optimization</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Version Control</h3>\n<p>Git has become the standard for version control, enabling teams to collaborate effectively.</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-dark\" style=\"background-color: #0d1117; color: #c9d1d9\"><div class=\"language-id\">bash</div><div class='code-container'><code><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #8B949E\"># Create a feature branch</span></div><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #C9D1D9\">git checkout -b feature/new-navigation</span></div><div class='line'></div><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #8B949E\"># Make your changes and commit</span></div><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #C9D1D9\">git add </span><span style=\"color: #79C0FF\">.</span></div><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #C9D1D9\">git commit -m </span><span style=\"color: #A5D6FF\">\"Add responsive navigation\"</span></div><div class='line'></div><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #8B949E\"># Push to remote</span></div><div class='line'><span style=\"color: #C9D1D9\">git push origin feature/new-navigation</span></div></code></div></pre>\n<h2>Component Deve